# kyma-dub — environment

# ============================================================
# Required: one Kyma key runs the whole pipeline
# ============================================================
# Transcription + translation + voice (eleven-v3) all go through this
# single key. Free credit at signup. Get yours at https://kymaapi.com
# (60-second signup, no card).
# ============================================================
KYMA_API_KEY=

# ============================================================
# Optional: ElevenLabs key (direct TTS path / deep fallback)
# ============================================================
# With this set, `--tts elevenlabs` voices straight from ElevenLabs
# (one less hop). Without it, voice runs through Kyma (same v3 quality).
# ============================================================
# ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=

# ============================================================
# Optional: Groq key (direct speech-to-text fallback)
# ============================================================
# GROQ_API_KEY=

# ============================================================
# Optional overrides
# ============================================================
# KYMA_DUB_BASE=https://api.kymaapi.com
